title: Renaming Rows
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Picking //rename// on a Conflicts row reveals an input next to the choice.  Type the new title; the row validates live:

* Empty title -- red, ''Apply'' disabled until fixed.
* Title matches an existing tiddler -- red, ''Apply'' disabled.
* Title matches another row's rename target -- red on both rows, ''Apply'' disabled.
* Otherwise -- green check.

Switching away from //rename// (back to //skip// or //overwrite//) clears the new-title input.
